---
// /masterclass page body — REBUILT as a clone of the homepage design.
// Every section now uses the homepage's bf-* section PATTERNS (Hero stage,
// HeroSplit 50/50, AboutBill 50/50, Reviews video+wall, MegaBento-style card
// grid, HelpGrid card grid, YoutubeCta dark-grainient device CTA, bf-faq
// accordion) with this page's VERBATIM copy re-homed into them.
//
// PRESERVED EXACTLY (unchanged from the prior page):
//   - the masterclass HERO + bento stage
//   - BOTH PRICING blocks (#pricing / #pricing2)
//   - all copy, images, links, the 8 written reviews, 21 screenshot reviews,
//     6 session points, foundation/pro feature lists, the 14 FAQs.
//
// The page wrapper (src/pages/masterclass/index.astro) supplies main.bf-page
// + CardNav + Footer + Islands. Grainient fills mount on [data-grainient].
